sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant C as Client
  participant G as API Gateway
  participant U as Upstream Contract
  participant B as banking-admin

  C->>G: POST /api/v1/ledger/entries
  G->>G: auth boundary check
  G->>G: resolve correlation id
  G->>U: postLedgerEntries(payload, correlation_id)
  U->>B: POST /banking_admin/api/v1/ledger_entries

  alt success
    B-->>U: 201 ledger response
    U-->>G: 201 ledger response
    G-->>C: 201 passthrough
  else duplicate/idempotency conflict
    B-->>U: 409 duplicate_reference
    U-->>G: 409 duplicate_reference
    G-->>C: 409 passthrough
  else unbalanced/validation
    B-->>U: 422 error envelope
    U-->>G: 422 error envelope
    G-->>C: 422 passthrough
  end

  Note over G,C: X-Correlation-ID returned in every response
